	<Title>
		Lupus: How does it affect the kidneys?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Lupus can cause inflammation of the kidneys, which can impair their function.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		How does lupus affect my kidneys?
	</Question>
